lead_paragraph: Renault's Jolyon Palmer and Manor's Rio Haryanto were handed three place grid penalties for the Austrian Grand Prix on Saturday for failing to slow for yellow warning flags in qualifying.

headline.print_headline: Palmer and Haryanto Handed Grid Penalties
headline.main: Palmer and Haryanto Handed Grid Penalties
